Senator Josh Hawley joins C&B to discuss the Supreme Court nominee, the W.H. attacks on him, Ukraine, the Olympics in China, WH/Big Tech censorship, the failed Biden agenda, and the Chiefs' AFC championship loss. DeSantis campaign produces flip-flop Fauci ad. Former Navy SEAL Jack Carr breaks down the strike on ISIS. C&B take calls to end the show.
